  "prompt": "How much is hootsuite?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Hootsuite offers various pricing plans tailored to different needs:\n\n1. **Free Plan**: Includes basic features, up to 2 social accounts, and limited posting capabilities.\n2. **Professional Plan**: Starting at around $19 per month, this plan includes features such as up to 10 social accounts, scheduling posts, and detailed reporting.\n3. **Team Plan**: Starting at approximately $99 per month, it offers up to 20 social accounts, custom analytics, team collaboration tools, and more.\n4. **Business and Enterprise Plans**: These are higher-tier plans with more comprehensive features and custom pricing based on specific requirements. \n\nPricing can vary and may be subject to changes, discounts, or promotions. Additionally, Hootsuite commonly offers a 30-day free trial for its paid plans.\n\nFor the most current and precise pricing details, I recommend checking Hootsuite's official website or contacting their sales team.",
